===================================================

On this map I focus on the details, so I hope you enjoy it,
there're 6 types of arenas that you can choose manualy (green button),
So go on and fight, other you're going to be hunted.
Flash and Smoke randomly, I recomend to play with humans
(but it's possible to play with BOTs)
enjoy!

===================================================
- 32 spawnpoints
- Enable HDR
- 6 types of arenas
===================================================
comment, vote and download XD!
